            . I am fifteen years old. I was with Jane Brown, and in <placeName id="t18280410-181-crimeloc974">Duke-street, Manchester-square</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18280410-181-crimeloc974" type="placeName" value="Duke-street, Manchester-square"></interp>
