                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280410-181-off972 t18280410-181-crimeloc974"></join>, I saw the prisoner come and take the purse; I asked her to give it up - she struck me in the eye and ran away; my cousin called Stop thief! nobody stopped her - I then called out and she was stopped. She gave the money to another girl, who got away.</p>
